snippet.title: BrokenLore: DON’T WATCH - Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out the announcement trailer for BrokenLore: DON’T WATCH for a peek at the nightmare that awaits in this upcoming game in the BrokenLore horror series. BrokenLore: DON’T WATCH will be available on PC.

#IGN #Gaming
